# Bible Reading History Feature

## Requirements
- Track the history of Bible chapters read by the user
- Store the last 20 selected chapters in local storage
- Automatically select the most recent chapter when reopening the app
- Allow users to view their reading history
- Implement using Zustand with persist middleware for local storage

## Implementation Plan
- Create a new history store using Zustand
- Store an array of recent selections (book and chapter)
- Add functions to add new entries to history
- Limit history to 20 entries
- Update BibleContext to use the history store
- Create a UI component to display reading history
